        <td class="cell-iso">R</td>
        <td class="cell-mid dash">Not represented</td>
        <td class="cell-eu dash">-----</td>
        <td class="cell-eu note">No dedicated free-text description in EHDSCondition; but realized in the EU Core Condition profile.</td>
